snippet.title: The Double Life of Amber Heard is Completely Exposed
snippet.description:
In this video we are going to talk about some things you may not know about Amber Heard’s personal life or in short we would like to say that she is completely exposed.  

SUBSCRIBE FOR MORE : http://bit.ly/32rc7vI
___________________________________________

Amber Heard grew up in Texas horseback riding, fishing and hunting with her father when she was a teenager. She dropped out of high school and left her family behind to pursue a career in show business. Heard started out modeling in New York City but when she got tired of posing for pictures she left for Los Angeles to dive into acting.
